pddl.prompt:
You are the orchestrator. Your objective is to produce a PDDL domain and a PDDL problem that, when given to the FastDownwards solver, will achieve the global target configuration:
{environment->public_information (goal lines)}
You will receive the following agent outputs (natural-language fragments):
{fragment_vowel}
{fragment_consonant}
Integrate those fragments, keep actions of vowel_agent and consonant_agent distinct where appropriate, and produce a final PDDL domain and problem. Think step by step. Enclose the PDDL domain between <domain></domain> tags and the PDDL problem between <problem></problem> tags. Target FastDownwards (e.g., avoid language features unsupported by typical FD setups and include clear action definitions and types).
